title: Andy Williams - Love, Andy (1967 Reel to Reel Transfer)
description:
Andy Williams - Love, Andy (1967 Reel to Reel Transfer)

Transferred a copy of this album for a friend, noticed it was not posted. So here we go!

320Kbps MP3's including case and tape scans.

Tape was played on a vintage Akai 4400, direct to CD on a Pionner PDR 555-RW, then ripped to the files you get here. MP3's will not have much for tags, if any. There, that's my disclaimer.
